&lt;p&gt;Are you the kind of person that thrives on providing excellent nursing care and getting the basics right?&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Is making a difference to your patients important to you? Are you a reliable, hard working person?&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;If your answer to these questions is yes, the Staff Nurse role on Ward 20 - Elective Surgery may be right for you.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Our patients can have complex care needs but what is common is how much they come to trust and rely on our great team.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;To be in this field of work you need to REALLY care. The job is very rewarding as well as demanding at times. in return for your hard work and commitment we offer a range of employee benefits for development and progression.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Flexible working part time and full time available&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
